Blog Application
================

----------
What is it
----------
This is Scooter-powered blog application. 
See http://www.scooterframework.com/docs/blog.html for more details.

-------------------
How to run blog app
-------------------

Run blog with default port 8080
linux/mac>%JAVA_HOME%/java -jar tools/server.jar examples/blog
windows  >$JAVA_HOME/java  -jar tools/server.jar examples/blog

Run blog installed in user home directory with port 9090
linux/mac>%JAVA_HOME%/java -jar tools/server.jar /home/joe/blog 9090
windows  >$JAVA_HOME/java  -jar tools/server.jar /home/joe/blog 9090

Note: "JAVA_HOME" must point to a JDK. This is required by Scooter's autocompiler.
